{"title":"SRAM & Campy Shift Better on Silca Pro-Spec 3D-Printed Titanium Derailleur Hangers","link":"https://bikerumor.com/silca-3d-printed-titanium-derailleur-hanger-fits-more-bikes/","date":1706623200000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_more-fitment-options-available-now.jpg\" alt=\"Silca 3D-printed titanium derailleur hanger gets more fitment options to work with Shimano, SRAM &amp; Campagnolo\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_more-fitment-options-available-now.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_more-fitment-options-available-now-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_more-fitment-options-available-now-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_more-fitment-options-available-now-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_more-fitment-options-available-now-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_more-fitment-options-available-now-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_more-fitment-options-available-now-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Last fall, Silca released their Tour de France Stage-winning hollow 3D-printed titanium derailleur hangers to the general public. But they were mostly limited to riders with Shimano drivetrains or UDH-equipped bikes – seriously limiting on-road applications. Well, Silca listened. And after quickly selling out those initial ti hangers, they are back with universal fits for 9 popular road &amp; gravel bike makers. And the original run are available again too. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Do you think an $85-99 titanium replacement derailleur hanger will improve your bike’s shifting?</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Silca 3D-printed titanium derailleur hanger fits more bikes</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_a-batch-of-UDH-Shimano-hangers.jpg\" alt=\"Silca 3D-printed titanium derailleur hanger, UDH for Shimano direct-mount\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_a-batch-of-UDH-Shimano-hangers.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_a-batch-of-UDH-Shimano-hangers-297x178.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_a-batch-of-UDH-Shimano-hangers-800x480.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_a-batch-of-UDH-Shimano-hangers-120x72.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_a-batch-of-UDH-Shimano-hangers-768x461.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_a-batch-of-UDH-Shimano-hangers-1536x922.jpg 1536w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<figcaption>(Photos/Silca)</figcaption>        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Silca 3D-printed titanium derailleur hanger, UDH for Shimano direct-mount\" /><figcaption>(Photos/Silca)</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Silca 3D-printed titanium derailleur hanger, UDH for Shimano direct-mount\" /><figcaption>(Photos/Silca)</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Developed as a project to improve the shifting on WorldTour road bikes… a lighter, stiffer hanger upgrade promising faster, more precise shifts for your road, gravel, and mountain bikes…</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Silca claims that “<em>modern electronic derailleurs shift so fast and with such force that conventional hangers made from low-grade aluminum plates will flex up to 4 degrees during a shift, resulting in less precise, noisier, and slower shifting. Traditional hangers also bend easily, even in minor incidents, resulting in unnecessary bike changes and additional workload for mechanics.</em>“</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you had a Shimano derailleur, these direct mount hangers promised faster, more precise shifting. Silca promised a whopping 8-10x higher stiffness when using the direct mount ti hanger vs. a standard replaceable aluminum hanger and teh extra link on the derailleur. On a UDH-compatible bike, they said their hollow 3D-printed titanium hanger was “5-6x stiffer than conventional aluminum hangers”. We assume those quoted  UDH gains will apply to their new universal fit derailleur hangers for more road and gravel bikes, too.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sounds like a no-brainer upgrade, right?</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_Univeral-Fit-hangers-for-UDH-bikes-in-the-printer.jpg\" alt=\"Silca 3D-printed titanium derailleur hangers in the printer\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_Univeral-Fit-hangers-for-UDH-bikes-in-the-printer.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_Univeral-Fit-hangers-for-UDH-bikes-in-the-printer-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_Univeral-Fit-hangers-for-UDH-bikes-in-the-printer-800x533.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_Univeral-Fit-hangers-for-UDH-bikes-in-the-printer-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_Univeral-Fit-hangers-for-UDH-bikes-in-the-printer-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_Univeral-Fit-hangers-for-UDH-bikes-in-the-printer-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_Univeral-Fit-hangers-for-UDH-bikes-in-the-printer-720x480.jpg 720w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Silca 3D-printed titanium derailleur hangers in the printer\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Silca 3D-printed titanium derailleur hangers in the printer\" /></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Of course, the 3D-printed hanger is meant to be a sacrificial element that breaks before your frame does. But Silca assures that even thoufh their ti hangers are ultra-stiff, there’s still an internal structure designed to break before your frame.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>So, what’s new?</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><img width=\"2167\" height=\"2167\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_103-fits-Factor-road-bike-with-Shimano-direct-mount-derailleur.jpg\" alt=\"Silca 3D-printed titanium derailleur hanger for Factor\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_103-fits-Factor-road-bike-with-Shimano-direct-mount-derailleur.jpg 2167w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_103-fits-Factor-road-bike-with-Shimano-direct-mount-derailleur-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_103-fits-Factor-road-bike-with-Shimano-direct-mount-derailleur-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_103-fits-Factor-road-bike-with-Shimano-direct-mount-derailleur-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_103-fits-Factor-road-bike-with-Shimano-direct-mount-derailleur-768x768.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_103-fits-Factor-road-bike-with-Shimano-direct-mount-derailleur-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_103-fits-Factor-road-bike-with-Shimano-direct-mount-derailleur-2048x2048.jpg 2048w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<figcaption>100-series Direct Mount for Shimano</figcaption>        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Silca 3D-printed titanium derailleur hanger for Factor\" /><figcaption>100-series Direct Mount for Shimano</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Silca 3D-printed titanium derailleur hanger for Factor\" /><figcaption>100-series Direct Mount for Shimano</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"2167\" height=\"2167\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_204-fits-Giant-road-bike-with-SRAM-or-Campagnolo-derivetrain.jpg\" alt=\"Silca 3D-printed titanium derailleur hanger for Giant\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_204-fits-Giant-road-bike-with-SRAM-or-Campagnolo-derivetrain.jpg 2167w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_204-fits-Giant-road-bike-with-SRAM-or-Campagnolo-derivetrain-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_204-fits-Giant-road-bike-with-SRAM-or-Campagnolo-derivetrain-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_204-fits-Giant-road-bike-with-SRAM-or-Campagnolo-derivetrain-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_204-fits-Giant-road-bike-with-SRAM-or-Campagnolo-derivetrain-768x768.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_204-fits-Giant-road-bike-with-SRAM-or-Campagnolo-derivetrain-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Silca-3D-printed-derailleur-hanger_204-fits-Giant-road-bike-with-SRAM-or-Campagnolo-derivetrain-2048x2048.jpg 2048w\" />\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t<figcaption>200-series Universal Fit for SRAM, Campagnolo &amp; more…</figcaption>        <div>\n                \n                    \n                \n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Silca 3D-printed titanium derailleur hanger for Giant\" /><figcaption>200-series Universal Fit for SRAM, Campagnolo &amp; more…</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div>\n<figure><img alt=\"Silca 3D-printed titanium derailleur hanger for Giant\" /><figcaption>200-series Universal Fit for SRAM, Campagnolo &amp; more…</figcaption></figure>\n</div>\n                <div></div>\n        </div></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new bit here is, that Silca expand their offering for the same 9 bike makers as before. S, you can either get a 100-series Shimano direct-moutn-specific hanger. Or get a 200-series Universal Fit one that you can use with SRAM, Campagnolo, MicroShift, TRP, Ingrid, or whatever you have lying around…</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, there’s still the Shimano or Universal Fit option for UDH bikes. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>And they are all in stock again.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Or if you had a UDH-compatible frame, you could use one with either any conventional derailleur or a Shimano Direct Mount. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Silca 3D-printed derailleur hanger – Pricing, options &amp; availability</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Silca-3D-printed-titanium-derailleur-hanger-shifting-upgrade_UDH-universal.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Silca-3D-printed-titanium-derailleur-hanger-shifting-upgrade_UDH-universal.jpg\" alt=\"Silca 3D-printed titanium derailleur hanger shifting upgrade, UDH universal fit\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Silca-3D-printed-titanium-derailleur-hanger-shifting-upgrade_UDH-universal.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Silca-3D-printed-titanium-derailleur-hanger-shifting-upgrade_UDH-universal-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Silca-3D-printed-titanium-derailleur-hanger-shifting-upgrade_UDH-universal-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Silca-3D-printed-titanium-derailleur-hanger-shifting-upgrade_UDH-universal-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Silca-3D-printed-titanium-derailleur-hanger-shifting-upgrade_UDH-universal-768x768.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Silca-3D-printed-titanium-derailleur-hanger-shifting-upgrade_UDH-universal-1536x1536.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>UDH universal fit</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Silca-3D-printed-titanium-derailleur-hanger-shifting-upgrade_UDH-Shimano-Direct-Mount.jpg\"><img width=\"1800\" height=\"1800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Silca-3D-printed-titanium-derailleur-hanger-shifting-upgrade_UDH-Shimano-Direct-Mount.jpg\" alt=\"Silca 3D-printed titanium derailleur hanger shifting upgrade, UDH Shimano Direct Mount\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Silca-3D-printed-titanium-derailleur-hanger-shifting-upgrade_UDH-Shimano-Direct-Mount.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Silca-3D-printed-titanium-derailleur-hanger-shifting-upgrade_UDH-Shimano-Direct-Mount-297x297.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Silca-3D-printed-titanium-derailleur-hanger-shifting-upgrade_UDH-Shimano-Direct-Mount-800x800.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Silca-3D-printed-titanium-derailleur-hanger-shifting-upgrade_UDH-Shimano-Direct-Mount-120x120.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Silca-3D-printed-titanium-derailleur-hanger-shifting-upgrade_UDH-Shimano-Direct-Mount-768x768.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Silca-3D-printed-titanium-derailleur-hanger-shifting-upgrade_UDH-Shimano-Direct-Mount-1536x1536.jpg 1536w\" /></a><figcaption>UDH Shimano Direct Mount</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Silca 3DP Derailleur Hanger is available to fit 9 brands of bikes for $85 a piece. That then, includes Cannondale, Canyon, Cervelo, Factor, Giant, Pinarello, Scott, Specialized &amp; Trek. Pick from 100-series for Shimano or 200-series for Universal Fit for SRAM, Campagnolo or other drivetrains. UDH-compatible hangers are also available for $99 in Shimano-specific or Universal Fit.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://silca.cc/\" target=\"_blank\">Silca.cc</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/silca-3d-printed-titanium-derailleur-hanger-fits-more-bikes/\">SRAM &amp; Campy Shift Better on Silca Pro-Spec 3D-Printed Titanium Derailleur Hangers</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"1f0c5df4bb0262c0a165d3ac7fa930273443b8f93998bd3e7e2ae7cbfed53db2","category":"Cycling"}